{"tid":1517848,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人星期日去機場管制區/東澳古道鳩嗌！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:03:10.000Z","uid":20948,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5269b26335abd0a64274d256a1b72a2c65f0476a","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"小弟作爲一個鍾意遊山玩水<span style=\"color: green;\">玩飛機</span>嘅港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大嶼山都算熟悉，以前周不時去行山睇飛機。<br />\n最熱門近距離睇飛機升降南環路相信無需多講，一張圖講曬：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/D1ddDhb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1ddDhb.jpg&h=5a2dc2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過留意返行路都需時，交通唔方便，多數單車撚會玩得開心啲。<br />\n<strong>去玩嘅港豬記得唔好黑衫，你知班暴徒喺機場搞事隨時殃及無辜。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左攝影撚最鍾意去跑道之外，睇飛機第二熱點就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">東澳古道</span></span><br />\n路線如下：<br />\n喺東涌站搭巴士去滿東邨<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/z0k30rG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k30rG.jpg&h=b33ddcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後開始行山，大概步行45分鐘，就可以到達距離機場跑道最近嘅碼頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/0XbyDcA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XbyDcA.jpg&h=5f7bf900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度唔係機場範圍，以前喺附近玩drone低飛冇人理，不過亂咁飛其實好容易造成危險。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>千祈唔好飛過去機場跑道範圍，會造成安全威脅，飛機停飛</strong></span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>如果隻drone俾人射落黎，捉到人隨時監都有得坐！</ins></span>所以大家諗清楚。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">不過我係機管局，見到隔離山有一堆drone飛黎飛去，都可能好驚你突然飛過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，介紹下呢個隱世打卡位，位於東澳古道嘅天文臺站，<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6QYpK1C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QYpK1C.jpg&h=d15021d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左望到曬飛機起飛降落，仲可以見到南環路嘅龍友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然小弟經常行山，但一堆人喺山嘅唔同位置鳩叫，<span style=\"color: blue;\">玩雷射show</span>都真係未試過，<br />\n希望大家一齊遊山玩水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，鼓勵大家買張平機票，即興去旅行。<br />\n如果唔買，想去機場counter即興飛都得，最緊要帶護照同少量行李。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1791e48cd7bf954f23d516b5df8342837e574e5","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"舊post推唔到開新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fc7f430a6d62dabc81fc863c8d8fef310a8021","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"544b6404f8679cce192f52807af26a75a5654732","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"16c10857bfd6978ce2c195075a1d13aec5ee82ed","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"098bb079eb57fcae7c12193161f6754cec96f635","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:00:23.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450b77438dafa8d6ba385920d5af77828f85e227","tid":1517848,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score